        <mxCell id="noteA" value="PERSISTENCE  — on 'Record Raw Files'
Write raw files + AI output to the credit-owned
store. The Queue is the system of record
(not the chat session)." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;size=14;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="600" y="1025" width="320" height="82" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="noteB" value="LOGGING  — on 'Call AI Review'
