audit trail. NexChat is a compute service,
not a store." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;size=14;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="940" y="1025" width="320" height="82" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="noteC" value="FAIL-SAFE (new) — on 'AI Review OK?'
